{"word":"Succoth","slug":"succoth","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Succoth</b> <a href=\"#/H5523\">H5523</a> <br/> 1. A city probably east of the Jordan:<br/> - Jacob builds a house in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=33&verse=17'>Gen 33:17</a> <br/> - Allotted to Gad<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=13&verse=27'>Jos 13:27</a> <br/> - People of, punished by Gideon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=8&verse=8'>Jdg 8:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=8&verse=16'>Jdg 8:16</a> <br/> - Located near the Jordan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=46'>1Ki 7:46</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=4&verse=17'>2Ch 4:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=60&verse=6'>Psa 60:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=108&verse=7'>Psa 108:7</a> <br/> 2. First camping place of the Israelites on leaving Rameses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=37'>Exo 12:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=13&verse=20'>Exo 13:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=33&verse=6'>Num 33:6</a>"}]}